COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1205, L.D. 1800
42 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
43 number to read consecutively.
44 SUMMARY
445 This amendment makes technical changes to the bill and changes the title. The
456 amendment applies the substantive provisions of the bill to health maintenance
467 organizations in the appropriate chapter of the Maine Insurance Code.
